The '''''Bottom Line''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] that was owned by an unidentified [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]]. When the vessel landed on the [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of the [[Tinnell]]s, [[Purr]] stowed away on board.

